WEBVTT

00:03:56.002 --> 00:04:00.517
emerging at 30 from the "... wasteland
of preparation into active life;"

00:04:01.057 --> 00:04:05.173
learning at 40 "... to close softly
the doors to rooms

00:04:05.197 --> 00:04:07.326
[I would] not be coming back to."

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:10.315
There I was.

00:04:11.885 --> 00:04:14.143
Of course, there we all are.

00:04:14.762 --> 00:04:17.200
Milton Glaser, the great graphic designer

00:04:17.224 --> 00:04:20.035
whose beautiful
visualizations you see here,

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:22.379
and who today is 85 --

00:04:22.403 --> 00:04:26.503
all those years "... a ripening
and an apotheosis," wrote Nabokov --

00:04:27.211 --> 00:04:30.669
noted to me that, like art and like color,